title: Best Of (KD calls NBA 2K rating "laughable," Pat Beverly takes shot at LeBron & AD for not making playoffs)
description:
00:00 Should KD be ranked below Giannis and the same as LeBron and Steph in NBA 2K23?
13:01 Pat Beverly on playing with LeBron and AD: "I made the playoffs last year, they didn't."
20:06 How wil Baker Mayfield do in Sunday's matchup against his former team in Cleveland?
27:13 Jalen Ramsey on matchup vs the Bills: "They good, but we good too."
